===Etymology===
Either from French ''[[chébec]]'', from Spanish ''[[xabeque]]'' (modern ''[[jabeque]]'') or Catalan ''[[xabec]]'', ultimately from Arabic {{ARchar|[[شباك|شبّاك]]}} (šabbāk) ‘small warship, fishing boat’.

